      • onRequestDynamicPermissionsResult

        void onRequestDynamicPermissionsResult(List<DynamicPermission> permissions,
                                       String[] dangerousLeft,
                                       List<DynamicPermission> specialLeft)
        This method will be called after requesting a set of permissions.
        Parameters:
        permissions - A list of all the required permissions.
        dangerousLeft - An array of dangerous permissions not yet granted or requested.
        specialLeft - A list of special permissions not yet granted or requested.
